Q: 飞机注册号为N808CE的飞机是哪一家公司的？
SQL: SELECT sd.supplier_name FROM aircraft_details ad JOIN supplier_details sd ON ad.supplier_id = sd.supplier_id WHERE ad.registration = "N808CE";
actual_SQL:
SELECT s.supplier_name
FROM aircraft_details a
JOIN supplier_details s ON a.supplier_id = s.supplier_id
WHERE a.pure_reg = 'n808ce'
LIMIT 50;
